  "description": "This is a Japanese-style adventure game based on the popular TV anime series <i>Neon Genesis Evangelion</i>. A girl named Mana Kirishima arrives at Tokyo-3 and studies in the same class with Shinji Ikari, the series' main hero. About the same time, a giant robot attacks the city. Is there a connection between the new student and the sudden assault?<br><br>Unlike the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=neon+genesis+evangelion\">two</a> <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=neon+genesis+evangelion+2nd\">previous</a> <i>Neon Genesis Evangelion</i> games, <i>K?tetsu no Girlfriend</i> is not an interactive movie. The player controls Shinji by selecting locations to travel to, looking at people, and talking to them. The locations are graphically represented as anime-style still screens. ",
